47
00:04:30,774 --> 00:04:32,997
So the only path left was to form a

48
00:04:34,752 --> 00:04:46,617
an advisory committee through a special act that gave us the ability to make recommendations that went to the mayor and from the mayor to the city council and then to the statehouse.

